{"tid":444153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（玩撈同好）岩岩出黎做野想買隻撈玩下","createTime":"2017-10-22T09:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T06:18:11.000Z","uid":121449,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"50a2399aa7bf987ffe21ab0e60660b896dc9c7b7","tid":444153,"uid":121449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩出黎做野<br />\n月入23K左右，扣左強姦金就得番22k<br />\n想入隻GTM黎玩下（新手版）<br />\n只想買行貨，唔買水貨，水貨怕有伏<br />\n想問下邊間有得做免息分期，定一炮過比好呢？<br />\n我個人覺得分期可以當儲里路係唔錯既選擇<br />\n各位親愛的師兄指教下小弟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/171445_106fed1f771c3ca1b31adc21772674ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F171445_106fed1f771c3ca1b31adc21772674ca.jpg&h=8e5be0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大大力屌我啦，如果我有錯<br />\n屌醒小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f3cc1075b043be0a472aceb1a1599a8af3b8cb","tid":444153,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/172527_f0a3419c5f2b3d85a70b32f36863ef75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F172527_f0a3419c5f2b3d85a70b32f36863ef75.jpg&h=dd4b171f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93ef0049cba0d9baf4cdcfb698922baac5d55114","tid":444153,"uid":121449,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/172527_f0a3419c5f2b3d85a70b32f36863ef75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F172527_f0a3419c5f2b3d85a70b32f36863ef75.jpg&h